name: AdataV18_Final
description:
A merging of various models (that for most of them are already merging of various models, so don't ask me for the exact number or % of models there)

The models I remember with relative good confidence being included are :

Wyvernmix6 (from an older custom merge that was merged in the final model)

cyberrealistic_v31

deliberate_v2

epicrealism_Purevolution

realisticVisionV20_20

majicmixRealistic_v6

fantasticmix_v65

Dreamshaper_6BakedVae

qgopromptingreal_qgoPromptingrealV1

AnalogMadness (not sure which version probably not the absolute latest)

in various % (probably most under 10% since there is other models that I i'm not sure about, and part of an older custom merge that I merged as well in that one)

But the result is good enough that I decided to post it, no fine tuning (mostly because I don't know how to do this), nothing special about it, just a good old massive merge that work quite well and produce quality images, aiming mostly at realistic and borderline photorealistic result as you could probably guess by the names of the merged models.
